  "orlando-fl": `Orlando siding warranty coordination: James Hardie 30-year non-prorated product warranty on fiber cement. Florida Product Approval (FPA) compliance is warranty-affecting; non-FPA products may fail warranty coverage at post-inspection discovery. Stucco over CMU has no manufacturer product warranty; contractor workmanship warranty typically runs 3-10 years. Annual inspection for stucco delamination from CMU substrate and biological-growth remediation is essential in Central Florida humidity. HPB landmark-approved materials in College Park and Winter Park have specific warranty considerations. Florida certified or registered contractor license (CGC/CRC at myfloridalicense.com) must be active throughout warranty period for enforceable claims under Florida Statute Chapter 489.`,
