  "sacramento-ca": `Sacramento siding warranty coordination: James Hardie 30-year non-prorated product warranty on fiber cement; Kynar fluoropolymer finish carries 25-year warranty suitable for Central Valley UV. Stucco has no manufacturer product warranty; contractor workmanship warranty typically runs 3-10 years. Expansive-clay foundation settlement in South Sacramento and Elk Grove is a common cause of premature stucco cracking; foundation-related damage is excluded from most siding warranties. Preservation Commission-approved materials in Midtown and Boulevard Park have specific warranty considerations. CSLB license (verifiable at cslb.ca.gov) must be active throughout warranty period. Annual inspection of stucco for crack propagation and efflorescence is prudent.`,
